  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the research study is to test a measurement tool that will determine the
      radiation dose people receive when they have been accidentally exposed to radiation. This
      test will be done using a small amount of blood and known dose of radiation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
